n =E2=80=9Cera of just plain meanness.=E2=80=9D Now, he
offered almost <em>no</em> criticism and made little effort to contextualiz=
e false or misleading statements with fact. As Darcy noted, =E2=80=9COutsid=
e the physical body, the Tapper of 2025 shared little in common with the pu=
gnacious Tapper of 2020.=E2=80=9D</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px=
;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">Of course, CNN=E2=80=
