n-bottom:0px;">Alas, the most devastating blow is still to come. In Novembe=
r, I
<a href=3D"https://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnVDJ4Z1lEQUt2Uktx=
clJLZ0dVa1A3TkJFNXZ3anhhbjF4Q2lobz0iLCJocmVmIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly9wdWNrLm5ld3MvY25=
ucy1leGlzdGVudGlhbC1wb3N0LWVsZWN0aW9uLXNlYXNvbi8_dXRtX2NhbXBhaWduPUluK3RoZS=
tSb29tKy0rU1VCU0NSSUJFUlMrJTI4MSUyRjIyJTJGMjUlMjlcdTAwMjZ1dG1fY29udGVudD1Jb=
itUaGUrUm9vbSstK1NVQlNDUklCRVJTKyUyODElMkYyMiUyRjI1JTI5XHUwMDI2dXRtX21lZGl1=
bT1lbWFpbF9hY3Rpb25cdTAwMjZ1dG1fc291cmNlPWN1c3RvbWVyLmlvXHUwMDI2dXRtX3Rlcm0=
